2005-01-16 Seiichi SATO <ssato@sh.rim.or.jp>

	* mlterm/ml_pty.c (ml_pty_new): In the forked pty process, reset the
	signal handler for SIGPIPE. (SIG_IGN -> SIG_DFL)

