	* In XDND, drop via UCS2 (as "text/unicode") is supported.

2002-11-12  MINAMI Hirokazu  <minami@chem.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp>

	* XDND code cleanup/separation. added x_dnd.(c|h) .

2002-11-11 Seiichi SATO <ssato@sh.rim.or.jp>

